<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 12:13:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时回避了有关与以色列媒体交谈的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dodges-questions-about-talking-to-israeli-media-in-cnn-interview/0000018f-9ff9-da3b-a7ff-9ffd1c950000</link><description>“他们没有告诉你的是，我已经与以色列媒体举行了 20 到 15 场新闻发布会。他们可以问任何他们想问的问题，他们也确实这么做了。”内塔尼亚胡对杰克·塔珀说道，塔珀专门询问的是采访而不是新闻发布会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:56:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dodges-questions-about-talking-to-israeli-media-in-cnn-interview/0000018f-9ff9-da3b-a7ff-9ffd1c950000</guid></item><item><title>世俗的耶路撒冷人已经成为一个垂死的品种。他们应该对这座城市失去信心吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/secular-jerusalemites-have-become-a-dying-breed-what-should-they-do-to-survive/0000018f-9af3-da3b-a7ff-9bff0f300000</link><description>耶路撒冷世俗的黄金时代在 20 世纪 90 年代初结束，如今，非宗教人士占首都居民的比例不到十分之一。一些人警告说，世俗居民需要采取“少数派心态”</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:37:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/secular-jerusalemites-have-become-a-dying-breed-what-should-they-do-to-survive/0000018f-9af3-da3b-a7ff-9bff0f300000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙战争的阴影下，哥伦比亚大学未来全球领导人的毕业典礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/inside-columbias-graduation-ceremony-for-future-leaders-in-the-shadow-of-the-gaza-war/0000018f-9a0d-d264-a1bf-de9fe0ab0000</link><description>在上周的毕业典礼上，在距纽约市警察戒备的哥伦比亚大学校园近 100 个街区的一个体育场馆中，学生们为加沙举行的抗议活动仍在继续，而那些提到乌克兰战争等其他冲突的人遭到了嘘声</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/inside-columbias-graduation-ceremony-for-future-leaders-in-the-shadow-of-the-gaza-war/0000018f-9a0d-d264-a1bf-de9fe0ab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队对加沙人的勒索活动：“联系我们，否则我们会说你向哈马斯举报了你的邻居”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/contact-us-or-well-say-you-reported-your-neighbors-to-hamas/0000018f-9fc0-d8f6-a3ef-9feceaf20000</link><description>以色列军队已开始公布有关加沙人的身份细节，称其为哈马斯安全总局监视平民； 《国土报》的军方消息人士：军队已获得此次行动的法律许可</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:37:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/contact-us-or-well-say-you-reported-your-neighbors-to-hamas/0000018f-9fc0-d8f6-a3ef-9feceaf20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙一半以上的基督徒已经离开，教会对社区的未来感到担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/over-half-of-gazas-christians-have-left-the-church-is-fearful-for-the-communitys-future/0000018f-9f9b-d35f-a1df-dfdbeab70000</link><description>耶路撒冷宗主教自战争开始以来首次访问加沙的一座教堂，并会见了住在教堂内的家庭</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:11:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/over-half-of-gazas-christians-have-left-the-church-is-fearful-for-the-communitys-future/0000018f-9f9b-d35f-a1df-dfdbeab70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理本格维尔在访问圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺时谴责加沙援助和承认巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-ben-gvir-rails-against-gaza-aid-recognition-of-palestine/0000018f-9f98-d6da-a1cf-ffba05300000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长本-格维尔表示，西班牙、挪威和爱尔兰承认巴勒斯坦国，这是对哈马斯的奖励</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:39:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-ben-gvir-rails-against-gaza-aid-recognition-of-palestine/0000018f-9f98-d6da-a1cf-ffba05300000</guid></item><item>