上传了蒙着眼睛的巴勒斯坦人的帖子，并附有嘲讽的标题——军方称这“不符合以色列国防军的价值观”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 20:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-deputy-mayor-posts-photos-with-blindfolded-shackled-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-9c15-d6da-a1cf-ff379d6b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于供应短缺和以色列袭击造成的不安全局势，联合国停止在拉法分发粮食</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/un-halts-food-distribution-in-rafah-due-to-supply-shortages-insecurity-from-idf-strikes/0000018f-9c9a-da3b-a7ff-9f9fb1f60000</link><description>联合国表示，加沙约有 110 万人（近一半人口）面临灾难性的饥饿，该地区正处于饥荒的边缘。自5月6日以色列入侵拉法以来，人道主义物资危机在两周内加剧</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/un-halts-food-distribution-in-rafah-due-to-supply-shortages-insecurity-from-idf-strikes/0000018f-9c9a-da3b-a7ff-9f9fb1f60000</guid></item><item><title>“让战争机器挨饿”：加州大学圣克鲁斯分校的工人罢工声援亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/workers-at-uc-santa-cruz-go-on-strike-in-solidarity-with-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-9bf8-da35-a3af-dffa0a620000</link><description>周一，数百名罢工工人在加州大学学校集会，重点关注该州加沙营地的“警察镇压”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/workers-at-uc-santa-cruz-go-on-strike-in-solidarity-with-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-9bf8-da35-a3af-dffa0a620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡已经彻底迷失方向了吗？或许。但也许是故意的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/has-netanyahu-completely-lost-his-bearings-maybe-but-maybe-its-intentional/0000018f-9bb6-da35-a3af-dfbeacb70000</link><description>人们很容易说，以色列是由一个在严重的政治胁迫下绝望的人领导的，他似乎患有相互交织的综合症，这些综合症曾困扰着他之前的路易十四和沙贝泰·兹维等人。好吧，如果它真的被领导的话</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 18:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/has-netanyahu-completely-lost-his-bearings-maybe-but-maybe-its-intentional/0000018f-9bb6-da35-a3af-dfbeacb70000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷，而不是海牙：以色列必须调查内塔尼亚胡在加沙犯下的危害人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-not-the-hague-israel-must-investigate-netanyahu-for-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-9bee-d6da-a1cf-fbeeec0d0000</link><description>回应国际刑事法院逮捕令请求的唯一有效方法是召集以色列国家调查委员会，调查加沙人民是否被故意挨饿——而不是大喊反犹太主义和纳粹主义</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 17:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-not-the-hague-israel-must-investigate-netanyahu-for-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-9bee-d6da-a1cf-fbeeec0d0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 228 天：本-格维尔表示，以色列应该在战后控制加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-228-israel-should-control-gaza-after-the-war-ben-gvir-says/0000018f-9bfc-d264-a1bf-dfffe0c20000</link><description>以色列敦促“文明世界国家”反对国际刑事法院检察官的要求 ■ 国家安全顾问表示，美国即将与沙特阿拉伯达成升级关系的历史性协议 ■ 本-格维尔：以色列应该在战后控制加沙 ■ 以色列官员夺取广播以色列南部属于美联社的设备 ■ 以色列国防军称其在杰宁发起了反恐行动 ■ 战争进入 228 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-228-israel-should-control-gaza-after-the-war-ben-gvir-says/0000018f-9bfc-d264-a1bf-dfffe0c20000</guid></item><item><title>猛烈抨击国际刑事法院，以色列“官方”反对派与内塔尼亚胡腐败一样懦弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-21/ty-article/.highlight/slamming-icc-israels-official-opposition-is-as-craven-as-netanyahu-is-corrupt/0000018f-9bde-da35-a3af-dffe8eea0000</link><description>包括反对派领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德在内的绝大多数以色列议员在一封谴责国际刑事法院检察官汗预审令的信上署名。以色列议会中只有少数人明白，内塔尼亚胡是否“和辛瓦尔一样糟糕”，或者反之亦然，都无关紧要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-21/ty-article/.highlight/slamming-icc-israels-official-opposition-is-as-craven-as-netanyahu-is-corrupt/0000018f-9bde-da35-a3af-dffe8eea0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡警告国际刑事法院的汗：我不担心出国，“他应该担心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-warns-iccs-khan-im-not-concerned-over-going-abroad-he-should-be-worried/0000018f-9b5e-dce9-a1cf-ffde9c400000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡驳回了国际刑事法院针对他和国防部长加兰特的逮捕令申请，称其为“热门工作”，并将其与 9 月 11 日后对乔治·布什或二战后对富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福发出逮捕令进行比较</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-warns-iccs-khan-im-not-concerned-over-going-abroad-he-should-be-worried/0000018f-9b5e-dce9-a1cf-ffde9c400000</guid></item></channel></rss>